verbose_text: The theoretical HCl conversion percentage under the present operation conditions was calculated to be about 93% (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), and the present single-step conversion value is about 87% by H-RuO 2 / P25, much higher than the results of SBA15 (61%), active carbon (40%), pure anatase (57%), rutile TiO 2 (54%) and I-RuO 2 / P25 (77%), implying that P25 is a better support to load RuO 2.
evidence: P25 is a better support to load RuO 2
